text: Eleven is a compilation album by German rock group Reamonn. It was released on 27 August 2010 through Island Records/Universal Music Group. The album was certified Gold in Germany in 2011, and has charted in Germany, Austria, Switzerland and Greece. ==Promotion== "Yesterday" was released as the lead single to promote the album on 7 August 2010.
